gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Spurs 113, Timberwolves 112
gameRecap.excerpt: The Spurs defeated the Timberwolves, 113-112. Devin Vassell recorded 25 points, four rebounds and five assists for the Spurs, while Victor Wembanyama added 23 points, 10 rebounds, six assists and two blocks in the victory. Anthony Edwards tallied 32 points, six rebounds and 12 assists for the Timberwolves in the losing effort. The Spurs improve to 10-36 on the season, while the Timberwolves fall to 32-14.
